  <brief_title>Analgesia for Positioning Hip Fracture Patients for Spinal Anesthesia</brief_title>
  <official_title>Fascia Iliaca Compartment Block Versus Fentanyl for Positioning Patients With Hip Fractures for Central Nervous Blockade: a Randomized Trial.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Asklepieion Voulas General Hospital</agency>
