    <time_frame>Group A: 5 minutes after intervention (fentanyl), Group B: 20 minutes after intervention (block)</time_frame>
    <description>It will be measured in &quot;minutes&quot;, from the start of positioning maneuvers to the spinal needle removal</description>
  </secondary_outcome>
  <secondary_outcome>
    <measure>Quality of patient's position</measure>
